 We assume the cost of multiplying two polynomial matrices with dimension
 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 and degree 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $O^{\sim}(n^{\omega}d)$
\end_inset

