 column degrees are bounded by the entries of a list 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{s}\in\mathbb{Z}^{n}$
\end_inset

.
 A column basis 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{T}\in\mathbb{K}\left[x\right]^{m\times r}$
\end_inset

